testsuite.name: com.womakerscode.meetup.service.RegistrationServiceTest

testcase.name: Should get an registration by id
Should get an Registration model by registration attribute
Should return empty when get an registration by id when doesn't exists
Should throw BusinessException when try to save a new registration with a registration duplicated
Should filter registrations must by properties
